sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as OVMS REST<br/>configurable/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC<br/>configurable/TCP HTTP2
    participant ModelMgr as ModelManager
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant S3 as S3/Azure/GCS<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over Client,OV: Flow 1: REST Model Inference
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (RBAC)
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward (TLS 1.2+)<br/>mTLS
    RBAC->>REST: HTTP (plaintext)<br/>localhost
    REST->>ModelMgr: Route to model
    ModelMgr->>OV: Execute inference<br/>In-process C++ API
    OV-->>ModelMgr: Inference result
    ModelMgr-->>REST: Response
    REST-->>RBAC: JSON Response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,OV: Flow 2: gRPC Model Inference
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>gRPC: gRPC/HTTP2 (plaintext)<br/>API Key (optional)
    gRPC->>ModelMgr: Route to model
    ModelMgr->>OV: Execute inference<br/>In-process C++ API
    OV-->>ModelMgr: Inference result
    ModelMgr-->>gRPC: Response
    gRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over ModelMgr,HF: Flow 3: Model Loading from Remote Storage
    ModelMgr->>S3: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Cloud credentials
    S3-->>ModelMgr: Model files
    ModelMgr->>OV: Load model<br/>In-process

    Note over ModelMgr,HF: Flow 4: HuggingFace Model Download
    ModelMgr->>HF: HTTPS git clone / download<br/>TLS 1.2+ / HF Token (optional)
    HF-->>ModelMgr: Model artifacts

    Note over Prom,REST: Flow 5: Metrics Scraping
    Prom->>REST: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP plaintext / No auth
    REST-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
